## Creating Migrations

### Generate Migration

```bash
# Create new table
rails generate migration CreateArticles

# Add column
rails generate migration AddPublishedToArticles published:boolean

# Remove column
rails generate migration RemoveBodyFromArticles body:text

# Add reference
rails generate migration AddUserToArticles user:references

# Create join table
rails generate migration CreateJoinTableArticleTag articles tags
```

### Migration File Structure

```ruby
# db/migrate/20251103000000_create_articles.rb

class CreateArticles < ActiveRecord::Migration[8.0]
  def change
    # Migration code here
  end
end
```

